text: Empty Sky is the debut studio album by Elton John and was released on 6 June 1969. It went to number 6 in the United States and number 30 in Canada. == Track listing == ;Notes * "Val-Hala" was titled "Valhalla" on the 1975 US reissue. * "Hay Chewed" was titled "It's Hay-Chewed" on the 1995 CD reissue. title: Empty Sky
